arts.ttl: York return to winning ways in style with big victory over Yeovil
arts.sum: Town had Finn Cousin-Dawson and Dominic Bernard sent off.

arts.ttl: New home puts New York City FC closer to Manchester City
arts.sum: The New York organization announced in April of this year that they will open their official home by 2027, but today the name of the first specific soccer stadium in ‘The Big Apple’ was announced. CEO Brad Sims said: “ This is a historic announcement for New York City FC, Etihad Airways and the city of New York .
